 v0.30‡-v0.37 Some changes and bughunts              to February 10th, 1997

           * S3M loader completly rewritten (now faster and smaller)
           # MANY bugs found and removed
           * GREAT optimaziation of the mixer (now 5 asm opcodes !)
           + Interpolation 1.grade integrated for testing

