 v0.38‡    Comletly rewriting the mixer                 February 15th, 1997

           * I start to rewrite the mixer from the scratch for including
             IT format and to make the player more functionable
           # bug removed in interpolation and optimized (now 10 asm opcodes)
           # IRQ above 7 will now accepted correct

